      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic work to be roadworthy. The engine currently runs but exhibits a persistent knock, and the transmission struggles to engage properly in higher gears. Externally, there is visible rust on the wheel arches and multiple significant dents and scratches across several panels. The interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics, making this a project car or a candidate for parts.",
