    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a world where engineering meets artistry. This isn't just a vehicle; it\u2019s a preserved moment in time, a sculpted silhouette that commands the gaze of every passerby. The cabin is a sanctuary of hand-stitched leather and polished timber, smelling faintly of old-world luxury and ambition. When the engine stirs, it doesn't just start\u2014it awakens with a melodic, rhythmic purr that promises effortless power and a connection to the road that modern, sterile cars have long forgotten. The finish is deep and lustrous, catching the light like a polished gemstone, reflecting a life of being cherished rather than merely driven. This is your invitation to own a masterpiece that feels less like a machine and more like a legacy, ready to turn every mundane errand into a cinematic journey.",
      "price": 46850.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle arrives in pristine, showroom condition, having been preserved with fastidious attention to detail and a rigorous maintenance schedule. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, reflects a level of care rarely seen on the market today. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this is an investment-grade opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
